features of our text editors are: 

Jframe -> menubar -> | file name
   |                 | Edit menu
   |-> Text Area

file menu -> | new file
             | open file
             | save file

edit menu -> | cut
             | copy
             | paste
             | select all
             | close 

open file -> file chooser -> select path -> click on open button -> copy and paste the text of file to text editor.

final touch

we wamt to make text area scrollable 
so our new structure is 

frame -> namubar -> ------
   |-> panel -> scroll pane -> text area